This volume offers the transliteration and translation of texts related to the figure of Dumuzi (specifically, the composition known as ***Dumuzi’s Dream***), particularly focusing on the analysis of formulaic structure of the text, presenting textual variants and some philological notes; the aim of the contribution is to offer a complete description of Dumuzi, insisting on his role in Mesopotamian mythological sources. 


